com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.WTabSet.TabMode

  • Packages that use WTabSet.TabMode 
    Package Description
    com.github.bordertech.wcomponents
    Contains the core components of the WComponent framework.

    • Uses of WTabSet.TabMode in com.github.bordertech.wcomponents

      Fields in com.github.bordertech.wcomponents declared as WTabSet.TabMode 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static WTabSet.TabMode WTabSet.TAB_MODE_CLIENT
      A tab mode where tab content is always rendered, and invoking the tab only results in a client-side switch.
      static WTabSet.TabMode WTabSet.TAB_MODE_DYNAMIC
      A tab mode where invoking the tab will perform an ajax request every time the tab is requested.
      static WTabSet.TabMode WTabSet.TAB_MODE_EAGER
      A tab mode where invoking the tab will perform an ajax request immediately after the page is loaded.
      static WTabSet.TabMode WTabSet.TAB_MODE_LAZY
      A tab mode where invoking the tab will perform an ajax request the first time the tab is requested.
      static WTabSet.TabMode WTabSet.TAB_MODE_SERVER
      Deprecated. 
      Use TAB_MODE_DYNAMIC instead as a like-for-like replacement or any other mode if it is more appropriate to the individual use case.
